        "content": "<p>Job Description: </p><ul><li>To provide support to related projects to ensure the timeliness and quality of the deliverables</li><li>To provide on-going maintenance support to existing application systems etc.</li><li>To forecast and engage project resources for projects</li><li>To provide advice, support and coordination in different stages of active projects and existing systems, e.g. enhancement and security audit etc.</li><li>To manage and coordinate with IT contractors and related parties in supporting new projects and existing systems.</li><li>To provide on-call support to tackle urgent system and application incidents for the supported systems. </li></ul><p>Requirements: </p><ul><li>Higher Diploma or above in Computer Science </li><li>At least 4 years in IT industry</li><li>2 years solid experience in system implementation and maintenance/ support </li><li>2 years solid experience in Project Management &amp; IT Service/ Outsourcing Management</li><li>Good communication skills</li><li>Good command in spoken and written English and Chinese</li></ul><p>If interested for the above position, please send detailed resume with current and expected salary as well as date of availability by sending email to <strong>applyjob@clts.com</strong></p><p> </p><p>For more job opportunity, please visit our website: www.clts.com</p><p> </p><p>The personal information is collected strictly for recruitment purpose only.</p>",
